quran[17]{c,v,t}:
  23,1,Rwose abemeramana barahiriwe
  23,2,Ba bandi bakora iswala zabo bibombaritse
  23,3,Na ba bandi birengagiza ibidafite akamaro (mu mvugo no mu bikorwa)
  23,4,Na ba bandi batanga Zakat (amaturo ya ngombwa)
  23,5,Na ba bandi barinda ibitsina byabo (ntibishore mu busambanyi)
  23,6,"Uretse gusa ku bagore babo cyangwa ku bo bafiteho ububasha (abaja), kuko kuri bo batabigayirwa"
  23,7,"Ariko abazashaka kwinezeza ku batari abo (bavuzwe), rwose abo bazaba batandukiriye"
  23,8,Na ba bandi barinda ibyo baragijwe kandi bakubahiriza amasezerano
  23,9,"Na ba bandi bahozaho iswala (y’itegeko, bakazikorera ku bihe byagenwe)"
  23,10,Abo ni bo bazungura
  23,11,"Bazazungura Firidawusi (Ijuru risumba ayandi), bakazaribamo ubuziraherezo"
  23,12,Kandi mu by’ukuri twaremye umuntu (Adamu) tumukomoye mu ibumba ry’umwimerere
  23,13,Maze tumuha kororoka (kw’abamukomokaho) binyuze mu ntanga (twashyize) mu cyicaro gitekanye (nyababyeyi)
  23,14,"Hanyuma intanga (tuyiremamo) urusoro rw’amaraso, hanyuma (tururemamo) ikinyama, muri icyo kinyama turemamo amagufa, maze amagufa tuyambika umubiri, hanyuma (duhuhamo roho) tugihindura ikindi kiremwa (kigaragaza ishusho). Bityo, ubutagatifu ni ubwa Allah, Umuremyi uhebuje"
  23,15,"Nyuma y’ibyo, mu by’ukuri muzapfa"
  23,16,Hanyuma (nanone) muzazurwa ku munsi w’imperuka
  23,17,"Rwose twaremye ibirere birindwi bigerekeranye (tubishyira) hejuru yanyu, kandi ntabwo tuyoberwa ibyo twaremye (cyangwa ngo tubyibagirwe)"